Version 1beta7 - released 2014-01-15
* fixed bug, where empty and default language strings were saved (reported by
  simpleSolutions.dk)

Version 1beta6 - released 2014-01-12
* fixed bug, where category names with an underscore were not recognized
  (reported by tanavots)

Version 1beta5 - released 2013-12-20
* improved security wrt. XSS and CSRF
* lifted requirements to PHP 5.1
* removed translation-hints support
* removed config option folder_download
* added support for XH 1.6
* added config option translate_fullscreen
* added buttons to (de)select all modules for zipping
* added version.nfo
* added metaconfig.php for XH 1.6
* added plugin icon
* added Polish translation (contributed by learnandcode)
* updated English and added German manual
* refactored to MVC architecture
* improved QA (Phing, PHPCS, PHPCI, PHPUnit, PHPDoc)

Version 1beta4 - released 2011-11-04
* changed use_defaults to default_translation (inspired by svasti)

Version 1beta3 - released 2011-11-01
* fixed bug regarding translation-hints for the core

Version 1beta2 - released 2011-11-01
* changed download language pack to save language pack and display URL for
  copy&paste (suggested by Tata)
* updated manual accordingly
* made some minor enhancements

Version 1beta1 - released 2011-11-01
* added possibility to translate core language strings
* fixed bug regarding pluginloader translations
* added possibility to download properly arranged zip file as language pack for
  selected plugins
* added copyright section to the translated language files
* added configuration options and i18n
* added manual
* made several minor enhancements

Version 1dev1 - released 2011-10-30
* initial release
